Package: salad
Type: Package
Title: Simple Automatic Differentiation
Version: 1.0 
Date: 2024-06-07
Authors@R: person("Hervé", "Perdry", email = "herve.perdry@universite-paris-saclay.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Hervé Perdry <herve.perdry@universite-paris-saclay.fr>
Description: Defines an S4 class for automatic differentiation.
  The class handles both vector and matrices. The method used is forward automatic differentiation. 
  In most cases, functions written without automatic differentiation in mind can be 
  used with no change. 
